node.text: I’m partnering with @dermstore to show you some of my all time favorite skin care products and you will have a chance to win them all in this giveaway!  To enter my giveaway and win up to $1,000 in my favorite @dermstore products, all you have to do is follow @dermstore and comment under their post with the photo of me and comment with your favorite beauty emoji! Easy enough right!? You guys will LOVE these products! #Dermstorepartner

node.text: “I’m glad we didn’t listen, look at what we would be missing. They said, I bet they’ll never make it, but just look at us holding on. We’re still together, still going strong. You’re still the one.” ❤️ Happy 2 year anniversary honey! Love you and our little family more than anything in the world. “I’m so glad we made it, look how far we’ve come my baby.” ❤️

node.text: Vegas photo dump! We had so much fun in Vegas celebrating Stassi’s birthday with the babies! There was so much to do with them and we had the best time!! We definitely learned some lessons on our first trip with Cruz & Hartford! lol Thanks so much @phvegas for the fabulous stay! We can’t wait to come back. ❤️ #phabulous
